This is a simple URL shortener written in ruby on Sinatra 
and using SQLite as the backend database.

Usage: clone the repository and run

ruby lilurl.rb

to start the web server. Navigate to 

http://localhost:4567

or http://your.domain:4567

to view the site.

Dependencies: ruby >= 1.9.2, sqlite3 
Gems: rubygems, sqlite3, sinatra, digest/sha1
